videos.headline: Bryce Young finds Cameron Latu in the end zone for 12-yard TD pass
videos.description: Bryce Young completes his 10th straight pass to start the game, finding Cameron Latu for a touchdown.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Bryce Young finds Cameron Latu in the end zone for 12-yard TD pass) 2021/11/13 ESHEET

videos.headline: Alabama blocks punt to get incredible field position
videos.description: Alabama's Dallas Turner deflects New Mexico State's punt straight into the air, and the Crimson Tide recover with great field position.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Alabama blocks punt to get incredible field position) 2021/11/13 ESHEET

videos.headline: Robinson muscles his way into the end zone for a Bama TD

videos.headline: Bryce Young throws 5 TDs in Alabama's win
videos.description: Bryce Young passes for 270 yards and five touchdowns as Alabama routs New Mexico State 59-3.

tracking.trackingName: COM_NCF Highlight (Bryce Young throws 5 TDs in Alabama's win) 2021/11/13 ESHEET Sotfull

videos.headline: Saban happy with Tide's response after close call
videos.description: One week after No. 2 Alabama getting all it could handle from LSU, Nick Saban says he's pleased with the way his team bounced back.

videos.headline: Young gives all the credit to Tide's offensive line
videos.description: On his career day being the first Alabama QB to throw five TDs in single half, No. 2 Crimson Tide's QB Bryce Young praises his big men up front for his success.

videos.headline: No. 2 Crimson Tide rolls over New Mexico State
videos.description: Alabama executes on both sides of the ball with QB Bryce Young recording five TDs and 270 passing yards in the first half of 59-3 win over the Aggies.
